<section class="grounds-hero">
  <div class="reveal">
    <p class="eyebrow">Free AI-Powered Coffee Grounds Reading</p>
    <h1>Read Your Grounds</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      In <em>The Genesis Protocol</em>, a coffee mug holds the memory of someone who died
      trying to reveal the truth. A pattern in the residue that everyone else overlooked.
    </p>
    <p class="lead" style="color: var(--ink-soft);">
      Tasseography &mdash; the ancient art of reading tea leaves and coffee grounds &mdash; has been practiced
      for centuries by those who understand that patterns hide in plain sight. Now, AI reads the
      patterns for you. Upload a photo and receive your free coffee grounds reading online, instantly.
    </p>
    <p class="lead" style="color: var(--ink-soft); font-weight: 600;">
      What does your cup hold?
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div id="grounds-form-card" class="grounds-form-card reveal">
    <h2>Upload your cup</h2>
    <p>Finish your coffee or tea. Photograph what's left. The patterns will speak.</p>

    <form id="grounds-form">
      <div class="upload-area" id="upload-area">
        <input
          type="file"
          id="cup-image"
          accept="image/jpeg,image/png,image/webp"
          capture="environment"
          aria-label="Upload a photo of your cup"
        />
        <div id="upload-placeholder" class="upload-placeholder">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="color: var(--ink-soft); opacity: 0.5;">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"/>
            <polyline points="21 15 16 10 5 21"/>
          </svg>
          <p style="margin-top: 12px; color: var(--ink-soft);">
            Tap to photograph your cup<br>
            <small>or drag and drop an image here</small>
          </p>
        </div>
        <img id="image-preview" class="image-preview" style="display:none" alt="Your cup" />
      </div>

      <button class="button" type="submit" id="grounds-submit">
        <span id="grounds-button-text">Reveal the Pattern</span>
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>

  <div id="grounds-loading" class="grounds-loading" style="display:none">
    <div class="grounds-spinner"></div>
    <p class="grounds-loading-text">Analyzing the pattern architecture&hellip;</p>
    <p style="color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 8px;">The residue speaks to those who know how to listen.</p>
  </div>

  <div id="reading-result" class="reading-result" style="display:none">
    <div class="reading-card reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--teal);">Your Reading</p>
      <div id="reading-text" class="reading-text"></div>
      <div class="share-row">
        <button class="button small ghost" id="share-copy">Copy Link</button>
        <a class="button small ghost" id="share-x" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Share on X</a>
        <button class="button small ghost" id="share-native" style="display:none">Share</button>
      </div>
      <div class="grounds-book-cta">
        <img src="/assets/book2-cover.webp" alt="The Genesis Protocol" class="grounds-book-cover" loading="lazy" />
        <div>
          <p style="font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 8px;">
            The patterns in your cup echo across centuries. Sarah Chen found something far more dangerous in hers.
          </p>
          <a class="button" href="{{ site.amazonBook2Url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Read The Genesis Protocol &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="email-capture" class="email-capture-card reveal" style="display:none">
      <p style="font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 4px;">
        Enjoyed your reading?
      </p>
      <p style="color: var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Get the free prequel to the series &mdash; plus your reading delivered to your inbox.
      </p>
      <form id="email-capture-form" class="email-capture-form">
        <div class="grounds-fields">
          <div class="grounds-field">
            <label class="sr-only" for="capture-email">Email address</label>
            <input
              id="capture-email"
              name="email"
              type="email"
              placeholder="you@email.com"
              required
              aria-label="Email address"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="grounds-field">
            <label class="sr-only" for="capture-name">First name</label>
            <input
              id="capture-name"
              name="firstName"
              type="text"
              placeholder="First name (optional)"
              aria-label="First name"
            />
